Package org.midica.ui.player.soundcheck

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SoundcheckChannelModel
    This is the model for the channel combobox in the soundcheck window.
    SoundcheckController
    This class provides the controller and event listener for the soundcheck window.
    SoundcheckInstrumentModel
    This class provides the model for the instruments table in the soundcheck window.
    SoundcheckInstrumentTableCellRenderer
    Cell renderer for the instruments/drumkits table in the soundcheck window.
    SoundcheckNoteModel
    This class provides the model for the note/percussion list in the soundcheck window.
    SoundcheckView
    This class defines the UI for the soundcheck window.
